title: #192: The War On Wikileaks with Soudjian, Wilson and Hagstrom
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome back Marriette Soudjain, Jeffery Wilson and Ally Hagstrom to discuss Julian Assange's arrest and who can we really trust in this day and age of misinformation! Thank you for your support!
